    "description": {
      "value": "<h2><span class=\"fontstyle2\">FULL TORQUE<br></span></h2>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Beginning when you choose this ladder at 1</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 6pt;\">st </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color: #000000;\">level, you can use Strength in place of Dexterity for all attack and damage rolls with ranged weapons. You cannot use this ability with thrown explosives. </span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Alternately, when wielding two-handed small arms, heavy weapons, or super heavy weapons, you can use Constitution in place of Dexterity for all attack and damage rolls. Select either Constitution or Strength as your primary juggernaut ability.</span></p>",
